{"tid":2186488,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府亂吹 旅遊做餌𠱁檢測  專家：外國主要睇確診數字","createTime":"2020-09-03T04:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T04:34:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aac1c1e7c60ea64b2099763fb1a8a9d3e88954cb","tid":2186488,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/G4LZ4YGJ3RE2RNXEHL6API2L6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FG4LZ4YGJ3RE2RNXEHL6API2L6Q%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3haFdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=54c38f94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FG4LZ4YGJ3RE2RNXEHL6API2L6Q%2F&h=6ee3a56e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/G4LZ4YGJ3RE2RNXEHL6API2L6Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n政府亂吹 旅遊做餌𠱁檢測 <br />\n專家：外國主要睇確診數字<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。排。本報更發現市民完成檢測後，可於短時間內再次預約「驗完再驗」，立法會議員狠批政府只顧造大檢測數字，嚴重浪費寶貴的醫療資源。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：硬銷大龍鳳 林鄭引譚德塞舊論<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7PnbGAQUGan_8jwljLHNlHzO_58=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L6AGJRYKIJGMRIH7AMDHX7KKOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7PnbGAQUGan_8jwljLHNlHzO_58%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL6AGJRYKIJGMRIH7AMDHX7KKOU.jpg&h=b8c5563e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林鄭月娥政府強推的全民檢測計劃，市民反應未見踴躍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n准驗完再驗篤數<br />\n<br />\n聶德權昨接受電台節目訪問時表示，港府早前已與部份地區商討旅遊氣泡安排，包括內地、日本、泰國等港人熱門旅遊地區是否仍要隔離14天，。。。。。。。。，但他其後承認，即使全民檢測多人參與，數據也只作參考。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：羅卓堯：政府態度敵對<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超表示，落實旅遊氣泡的指標，是疫情是否有效持續受控，「可以從確診個案數字去睇，其實好多地區都冇全民檢測，一樣照有旅遊氣泡，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另本報記者在前日完成檢測，並於昨日早上收到陰性檢測結果短訊後，隨即下午使用同一身份證號碼及電話號碼，成功預約下周日再次檢測，換言之，市民可「無限輪迴」，重複接受檢測，或有機會出現造數情況。<br />\n<br />\n本身是醫生的立法會議員郭家麒炮轟有關安排「離晒大譜，仲唔係畀晒機會（政府）篤數？」他指即使市民檢測後隨即感染武肺，一兩日內病毒量亦難以增至可被驗出陽性結果的水平。他促請當局停止相關做法及交代數據。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。發言人僅稱計劃宗旨是每人「一次檢測」，但若有人認為有需要，如接觸過高危群組可再次預約檢測。發言人沒透露預約系統如何知道市民曾否接觸高危群組，亦沒有披露重覆檢測的人數，只說「相信不會太多」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅化驗4.9萬樣本<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷認為，火眼實驗室化驗能力明顯未符公眾預期，要求政府交代化驗數字遠低於宣傳目標低的原因，否則會削弱計劃公信力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IOm3S7jCNBs3ZBRH3xswmb1m87s=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VP6GHNMWJVEMLGBHUWW2QFBLPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIOm3S7jCNBs3ZBRH3xswmb1m87s%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVP6GHNMWJVEMLGBHUWW2QFBLPI.jpg&h=38d3026d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聶德權（右）指市民如想到日本等地旅遊，就越多人參加全民檢測越好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jr2s3RkMg-hg-jjXg2ON-jCp2FE=/1782x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OEYT3APVJFGONPYSXBPEXBNTGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJr2s3RkMg-hg-jjXg2ON-jCp2FE%3D%2F1782x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOEYT3APVJFGONPYSXBPEXBNTGU.jpg&h=cbb7ad9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港府早前已與部份地區商討旅遊氣泡安排。"},{"pid":"8f4bdf96755bf7d427bb3489af3a152ba1d7629a","tid":2186488,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"其他國家見你全民檢測得三成準仲點會同你整旅遊氣泡"},{"pid":"7da5e7daddf68ad9769301c244db8f2b8093e4e9","tid":2186488,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T04:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c